Name: p01.secureprincipal
Version: 0.5.0
Summary: Principal based securitypolicy for Zope3 using built in security declarations
Home-page: http://cheeseshop.python.org/pypi/p01.secureprincipal
Author: Roger Ineichen, Projekt01 GmbH
Author-email: dev@projekt01.ch
License: ZPL 2.1
Description: This package provides a securitypolicy based on roles without groups for
        Zope 3 applications. The missing group support allows to implement a faster
        securitypolicy.
        
        
